title: #92Noon! Florio/Snob/Gallagher/JJ
description: Florio begins 92noon, followed by Stump the Snob to finish the hour, Vikings/NFL talkers thru the middle stretch, then Mike Gallagher starts the final hour with NBA opinions, and Vikings WR Justin Jefferson wraps the show!
